"Xem <ulink url=\"&policy-relationships;\">Debian Policy Manual, 7 \"Declaring "
"relationships between packages\"</ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><para>
msgid ""
"Here is a simplified description of package relationships: <placeholder type=\"footnote"
"\" id=\"0\"/>"
